title: Week 11 preview & Titans vs. Jaguars recap
itunes:title: Week 11 preview & Titans vs. Jaguars recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – welcome back Lindsay Rhodes as they go game-by-game breaking down each Week 11 matchup. Then, the heroes recap the Jaguars 19-13 victory over the Titans in a Thursday night showdown between two of the league’s most promising young quarterbacks.
